pageContext.description: Dimensions: Length: 90.5mm; Width: mouth 31.8mm; loop 9.5mm; Extant breadth mouth: 36; D. Socket 63.5,Central rib one face - off central on other; corners of body tending to rib emphasised; bulge in one side body and absence of much of upper moulding from the casting; socket end prob. v. narrow.
pageContext.surface: Dull varied green-brown surface - mainly dry; broken edges + flaking - pale grey-green; intact edge sharp; rest and part of mouth broken - ancient or recent?; craggy material adhering to walls of socket - remnants of core?
